{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was the first time I started realizing those were people in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, people like me and everybody else who died, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was-- this was one of the greatest scientists, as I understand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in charge of the children diseases at the University of Prague.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was really one of the great, great professors and doctors the world has ever seen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had-- Theresienstadt was something very unique, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- we had actors who put on plays at night in the barracks upstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And unfortunate, I was too young to really appreciate all this talent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was such-- such-- and plus, I was so goddamn tired working these-- you know, because we had to get up at four, five o'clock in the morning to clean the horses and then-- then putting them-- you know, put them on a wagon and go back.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we came back for lunch, take the horses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They ate better than we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because then we fed them-- and I used to grab a little oats occasionally, put it in a pocket and-- and do something with it, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We put it and boiled it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It tasted horrible, at least it filled your stomach, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- so we-- we took food from the horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We said, the hell with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Eat straw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was-- there were so many opportunities to-- to-- to-- to partake there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one thing I saw an operetta.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the reason I saw there was a Danish comedian was playing in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called 'The Fleidermouse' or 'The Bat, by Johann Strauss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And without costumes, without anything, but it was done so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then by the way, they had a children opera.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
